com.wowza.gocoder.sdk.api.monitor

Class WOWZStreamingStat

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.wowza.gocoder.sdk.api.monitor.WOWZStreamingStat

  • public class WOWZStreamingStat
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a sample of network bandwidth statistics collected during a broadcast session.
